[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1010[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1011[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Mock classifier that returns plausible classifications based
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1012[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     on simple signal statistics. NOT a real arrhythmia detector.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1013[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1014[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Production replacement: a trained 1D CNN or transformer model
